https://docs.fedoraproject.org/f28/system-administrators-guide/basic-system-configuration/System_Locale_and_Keyboard_Configuration.html

# See etc/locale.conf for locale configuration

Display the currently set locale

$ localectl status

$ localectl list-locales

# Setting the locale
$ localectl set-locale LANG=<locale name here>


# Listing Available Keymaps
$ localectl list-keymaps
